OL,2,MWhat's in a number plate?
OL,4,CPaul Battley
OL,5,CSun 10:30-10:50
OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GWhy are Irish number plates so much
OL,9,Glonger than British ones, despite the
OL,10,Gpopulation being much smaller? What
OL,11,Gletters can you use on a Greek number
OL,12,Gplate? How do you drive a
OL,13,GJapanese-registered car abroad, when
OL,14,Gthe number plate is full of kanji and
OL,15,Gkana? Why do some people give Belgian
OL,16,Gcars with five-character plates a wide
OL,17,Gberth? Are those supercars with Arabic
OL,18,Gnumber plates you see in West London
OL,19,Geven legal? I've always been a bit
OL,20,Gobsessed with vehicle registration
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
